==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Karpholite
<hw>Kar"pho*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ rice
straw + <ets>-lite</ets>: cf. F. <ets>carpholithe</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A fibrous mineral occurring in tufts of a
straw-yellow color. It is a hydrous silicate of alumina and
manganese.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

